                <p>We'll end with a solid set of feasible projects that have sufficient backers to be completed over the weekend. As some project may take fewer people and less time to complete, we'll also try to come up with a sensible schedule for spreading them out over the weekend. Anyone got a fancy algorithm for that?</p>
                <p>For the uninitiated - that'd be all of us really - we'll have a primer on the scope of Open Data and delineate what sorts of issues and applications you can address at Make.01. We'll also introduce you to some of Hong Kong's OpenData datasets, tools and applications currently available.</p>
