                        <p>The immediate purpose of Make.01 is to provide makers with a time, a venue and the collaborators for them to realize their Open Data related ideas. Make.01 is thus organized for the benefit and enjoyment of its participants as we believe that if you provide them with those bare essentials, beautiful and worthwhile things will happen.</p>
